    "We propose using permutation triggers to address these issues.",
    "A permutation trigger requires that multiple components not only all appear but also follow a specific order to activate the backdoor.",
    "If any component is missing or out of order, the backdoor remains inactive.",
    "Formally, let Σ = {σ 1, σ 2,.",
    ", σ n } be a set of n distinct trigger components and let s = (σ 1, σ 2,."
